@baseUrl = http://localhost:5239

### ==================== Membership Plans ====================

### List all active membership plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans

### Get plan details (Basic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans/1

### Get plan details (Premium)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans/2

### Get plan details (Elite)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans/3

### Create a new membership plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Student",
  "description": "Discounted plan for students with valid ID",
  "durationMonths": 6,
  "price": 19.99,
  "maxClassBookingsPerWeek": 2,
  "allowsPremiumClasses": false
}

### Update a membership plan
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Basic",
  "description": "Access to standard classes with limited bookings per week - Updated!",
  "durationMonths": 1,
  "price": 34.99,
  "maxClassBookingsPerWeek": 3,
  "allowsPremiumClasses": false,
  "isActive": true
}

### Deactivate a membership plan
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/membership-plans/1

### ==================== Members ====================

### List all members
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members

### List members with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members?search=alice

### List active members with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members?isActive=true&page=1&pageSize=5

### Get member details (Alice - has Premium membership)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1

### Get member details (Sofia - has Basic membership)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/3

### Register a new member
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Zara",
  "lastName": "Mitchell",
  "email": "zara.mitchell@example.com",
  "phone": "555-0901",
  "dateOfBirth": "1998-06-20",
  "emergencyContactName": "Tom Mitchell",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "555-0902"
}

### Update member profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@example.com",
  "phone": "555-0111",
  "emergencyContactName": "Bob Johnson",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "555-0112"
}

### Deactivate a member (member 7 - Olivia, has expired membership, no future bookings)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/members/7

### Get member's bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1/bookings

### Get member's bookings filtered by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1/bookings?status=Confirmed

### Get member's bookings with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1/bookings?page=1&pageSize=5

### Get member's upcoming confirmed bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1/bookings/upcoming

### Get membership history for a member
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1/memberships

### Get membership history for member with expired membership
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/7/memberships

### ==================== Memberships ====================

### Get membership details (Alice's active Premium membership)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/1

### Create a membership for a member (member 7 - Olivia, currently has expired)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": 7,
  "membershipPlanId": 2,
  "paymentStatus": "Paid"
}

### Cancel a membership
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/1/cancel

### Freeze a membership (member 2 - Marcus, Elite)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/2/freeze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "freezeDurationDays": 14
}

### Unfreeze a membership
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/2/unfreeze

### Renew an expired membership (membership 7 - Olivia's expired Basic)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/7/renew

### ==================== Instructors ====================

### List all instructors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors

### List instructors filtered by specialization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors?specialization=Yoga

### List active instructors only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors?isActive=true

### Get instructor details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors/1

### Create a new instructor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Rachel",
  "lastName": "Green",
  "email": "rachel.green@zenithfitness.com",
  "phone": "555-1005",
  "bio": "Experienced Zumba and dance fitness instructor with 5 years of experience.",
  "specializations": "Zumba, Dance, Cardio",
  "hireDate": "2024-01-15"
}

### Update an instructor
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Sarah",
  "lastName": "Martinez",
  "email": "sarah.martinez@zenithfitness.com",
  "phone": "555-1001",
  "bio": "Certified yoga instructor with 12 years of experience. Specializes in Vinyasa, Hatha, and Restorative yoga.",
  "specializations": "Yoga, Pilates, Meditation, Restorative",
  "isActive": true
}

### Get instructor's class schedule
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors/1/schedule

### Get instructor's schedule filtered by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instructors/2/schedule?from=2025-01-01T00:00:00&to=2027-12-31T23:59:59

### ==================== Class Types ====================

### List all class types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-types

### List class types filtered by difficulty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-types?difficulty=Advanced

### List premium class types only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-types?isPremium=true

### Get class type details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/class-types/1

### Create a new class type
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/class-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zumba",
  "description": "Dance fitness class with Latin-inspired music",
  "defaultDurationMinutes": 60,
  "defaultCapacity": 30,
  "isPremium": false,
  "caloriesPerSession": 400,
  "difficultyLevel": "Beginner"
}

### Update a class type
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/class-types/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Yoga",
  "description": "Vinyasa flow yoga focusing on breath, movement, and flexibility",
  "defaultDurationMinutes": 60,
  "defaultCapacity": 25,
  "isPremium": false,
  "caloriesPerSession": 280,
  "difficultyLevel": "AllLevels",
  "isActive": true
}

### ==================== Class Schedules ====================

### List all scheduled classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes

### List classes with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes?page=1&pageSize=5

### List classes filtered by class type (Yoga = 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes?classTypeId=1

### List classes filtered by instructor
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes?instructorId=1

### List classes with availability only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes?available=true

### Get class details (Yoga tomorrow)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/1

### Get class details (FULL HIIT class with waitlist)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/8

### Schedule a new class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classTypeId": 1,
  "instructorId": 1,
  "startTime": "2026-03-25T10:00:00",
  "durationMinutes": 60,
  "capacity": 20,
  "room": "Studio A"
}

### Update class details
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classTypeId": 1,
  "instructorId": 1,
  "startTime": "2026-03-25T08:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-03-25T09:00:00",
  "capacity": 25,
  "room": "Studio A"
}

### Cancel a class (cascade cancels all bookings)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/12/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cancellationReason": "Instructor called in sick"
}

### Get class roster (confirmed members)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/1/roster

### Get class waitlist
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/8/waitlist

### Get available classes in the next 7 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/classes/available

### ==================== Bookings ====================

### Book a class (member 3 Sofia - Basic plan, non-premium class)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classScheduleId": 1,
  "memberId": 3
}

### Get booking details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/1

### Cancel a booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cancellationReason": "Personal schedule conflict"
}

### Check in for a class
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/1/check-in

### Mark booking as no-show
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/1/no-show

### ==================== Business Rule Test Cases ====================

### TEST: Book a premium class as Basic member (should fail - member 3 Sofia has Basic plan)
### Sofia (member 3) tries to book Pilates (class 4, premium) -> should get 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classScheduleId": 4,
  "memberId": 3
}

### TEST: Book a full class (should go to waitlist)
### Book into FULL HIIT class (class 8, capacity 3, enrollment 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classScheduleId": 8,
  "memberId": 2
}

### TEST: Member with expired membership tries to book (member 7 Olivia - should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classScheduleId": 1,
  "memberId": 7
}

### TEST: Freeze membership with invalid duration (should fail - min 7 days)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/1/freeze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "freezeDurationDays": 3
}

### TEST: Create membership for member who already has active one (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": 1,
  "membershipPlanId": 3,
  "paymentStatus": "Paid"
}

### TEST: Register member under 16 (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Young",
  "lastName": "Person",
  "email": "young.person@example.com",
  "phone": "555-9999",
  "dateOfBirth": "2015-01-01",
  "emergencyContactName": "Parent Person",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "555-9998"
}
